# Agenda
Agenda API is a *short texts saving* service similar to its physical paper presence in your school.

# Group Login
allow the teacher to login **Agenda API**

## login Collection [/notes]
### List all Notes [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [{
          "id": 1, "title": "Jogging in park"
        }, {
          "id": 2, "title": "Pick-up posters from post-office"
        }]

## login [/login]
### Login [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        { "username": "jad", "password": "4234" }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
        "message":"hello world",
        "error":32,
        "success":true 
        }

## Note [/notes/{id}]
A single Note object with all its details

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Note to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Note [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-My-Header: The Value

    + Body

            { "id": 2, "title": "Pick-up posters from post-office" }

### Remove a Note [DELETE]
+ Response 204


